synopsis

     Carla is a girl of twenty years, with a sculptured body, cheerful, a lush sensuality When you decide to rent an apartment for Matteo, the man who is passionate, she meets Moira, the owner of the agency, which will include Carla in several erotic events . Matteo knows nothing, but I suspect Carla. And even if he go insane with jealousy at the thought of his girl in the arms of another, the same jealousy becomes more and more in love with her
